pos_examples: Now, cut board bastion into large part object_260 using highspeed-saw frame_9 with awood yew, surface fire, changing size from aboardsize object_50 to aboardsize dress_red through intermediate sizes aboardsize dress_red_34 and aboardsize object_50_29.
(cut-board-large bastion object_260 frame_9 yew fire object_50 dress_red_34 object_50_29 dress_red)

Once you are done, please saw board bastion into medium part object_260 using saw star_213 with awood yew, surface fire, changing size from aboardsize object_50 to aboardsize dress_red_34 through aboardsize object_50_81.
(do-saw-medium bastion object_260 star_213 yew fire object_50 object_50_81 dress_red_34)

First, do immersion varnish on part object_260 using immersion-varnisher socket to change color to acolour roof_11 with surface fire and then do grind on part object_260 using grinder kumquat_8 to change surface from surface fire to verysmooth, color from acolour roof_11 to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus kumquat to treatmentstatus kumquat_62.

(do-immersion-varnish object_260 socket roof_11 fire)
(do-grind object_260 kumquat_8 fire roof_11 kumquat kumquat_62)

The next step is to do plane on part object_260 using planer teddy to change surface from surface fire to smooth, color from acolour roof_11 to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus kumquat_62 to untreated.
